站務員「小穹（Sora）」是高捷少女計畫第一個推出的虛擬代言人，命名和髮飾來自於[[美麗島站|美麗島站]]地標「光之穹頂」。其中美麗島站也因為「光之穹頂」設計，先是在2011年時被地鐵資訊網站「Metrobits.org」視為全世界50個最美麗的地鐵站之一<ref name=micro>{{Cite web |url = http://mic-ro.com/metro/metroart.html |title = A guide to the fifty most beautiful subway systems in the world |author =  |date = 2011-12-01 |publisher = Metrobits.org |language = en |accessdate = 2015-01-16 |quote =  |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061202064053/http://mic-ro.com/metro/metroart.html |archivedate = 2006-12-02 }}</ref>，在2012年時更被美國旅遊網站「BootsnAll」評選為全世界最美麗的地鐵站第二名，僅次於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[蒙特利爾|蒙特利爾]]的[[戰神廣場站|戰神廣場站]]<ref name=BootsnAll>{{Cite web |url = http://www.bootsnall.com/articles/11-11/15-of-the-coolest-subway-stops-in-the-world.html?fb_comment_id=fbc_10150506755310130_24174480_10150724519595130#f106de176 |title = 15 of the Most Beautiful Subway Stops in the World |author = Isabel Eva Bohrer |date = 2011-11-08 |publisher = BootsnAll |language = en |accessdate = 2015-01-16 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140416125617/http://www.bootsnall.com/articles/11-11/15-of-the-coolest-subway-stops-in-the-world.html?fb_comment_id=fbc_10150506755310130_24174480_10150724519595130#f106de176 |archive-date = 2014-04-16 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

「小穹」的角色設定身高163公分、體重則是45.625公斤，生日10月16日<ref name="人物介紹-小穹">{{Cite web |url = https://www.facebook.com/K.R.T.GIRLS/photos/pb.1575613346002638.-2207520000.1421474852./1579519092278730/?type=3&theater |title = 《人物介紹-小穹》 |author = [[高雄捷運公司|高雄捷運公司]] |date = 2014-11-29 |publisher = [[Facebook|Facebook]] |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2015-01-16 |quote =  |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180327025752/https://www.facebook.com/K.R.T.GIRLS/photos/pb.1575613346002638.-2207520000.1421474852./1579519092278730/?type=3&theater |archivedate = 2018-03-27 }}</ref>，星座與血型分別是天秤座與B型<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.nownews.com/n/2014/11/21/1515322 |title = 高雄捷運看板娘小穹體重45.625　四捨五入最討厭！ |author =  |date = 2014-11-21 |publisher = [[今日新聞網|今日新聞網]] |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2015-01-16 |quote =  |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150123064159/http://www.nownews.com/n/2014/11/21/1515322 |archivedate = 2015-01-23 }}</ref>。其外表有著黑色長髮，主要穿著高雄捷運的藍綠色和白色設計的站務員制服、搭配迷你裙，衣服上的設計包括藍綠色的領口玫瑰和領口滾邊<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w92otIS6L2Y |title = 站務員「小穹」替高捷站台 網友：我戀愛了 |author = [[東森新聞台|東森新聞台]] |date = 2014-11-18 |publisher = [[YouTube|YouTube]] |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2015-01-16 |quote =  |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150124143533/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w92otIS6L2Y |archivedate = 2015-01-24 }}</ref>，另外在左手臂掛上高雄捷運標誌章<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/local/paper/840642|title =〈南部〉高捷虛擬站務員 今辦見面會|author =葛祐豪|date =2014-12-20|publisher =《[[自由時報|自由時報]]》|language =zh-hant|accessdate =2015-01-16|quote =|deadurl =no|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20141220140732/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/local/paper/840642|archivedate =2014-12-20}}</ref>。在「小穹」的背景設定中，她喜歡的公共藝術是美麗島站的「光之穹頂」，甚至每天通勤經過美麗島站是其繼續在高雄捷運工作的最大動力<ref name="超萌虛擬制服妹">{{Cite web |url = http://www.ettoday.net/news/20141118/427119.htm |title = 超萌虛擬制服妹「小穹」登場　高捷創意大獲好評 |author =  |date = 2014-11-18 |publisher = [[ETtoday_東森新聞雲|ETtoday 東森新聞雲]] |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2015-01-16 |quote =  |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150123060742/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20141118/427119.htm |archivedate = 2015-01-23 }}</ref>。

另外在人物設定中，她也喜歡浪漫而美好的事物、充滿人文氣息的環境和從事人文相關活動，尤其是本土文化與現代文學創作。在人物外表上雖然看似家庭條件優越的大小姐「高嶺之花」，但是遇到感興趣的事情就會變得相當主動。私底下是個善於交際且平易近人的女孩，但是討厭不衛生以及在捷運車站內飲食的人<ref name="高捷娘小穹開粉絲團">{{Cite web |url = http://www.ettoday.net/news/20141121/428720.htm |title = 高捷娘小穹開粉絲團首日破萬　網友拍桌： 三圍呢？ |author =  |date = 2014-11-21 |publisher = [[ETtoday_東森新聞雲|ETtoday 東森新聞雲]] |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2015-01-16 |quote =  |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150118060956/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20141121/428720.htm |archivedate = 2015-01-18 }}</ref>。她於大學中文系畢業後，原本希望能夠進入出版社或文化局工作，並因而搬到高雄市；但是在被美麗島站的「光之穹頂」設計震撼後，最終選擇進入高雄捷運公司工作<ref name = "人物介紹-小穹"/><ref name="宅男快來">{{Cite web|url =http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20141217/525663/applesearch/%E5%AE%85%E7%94%B7%E5%BF%AB%E4%BE%86%E3%80%80%E9%AB%98%E6%8D%B7%E6%9C%80%E8%90%8C%E7%AB%99%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86|title =宅男快來　高捷最萌站務員來了|author =涂建豐|date =2014-12-17|publisher =《[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]]》|language =zh-hant|accessdate =2015-01-16|quote =|deadurl =no|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20151208073105/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20141217/525663/applesearch/%E5%AE%85%E7%94%B7%E5%BF%AB%E4%BE%86%E3%80%80%E9%AB%98%E6%8D%B7%E6%9C%80%E8%90%8C%E7%AB%99%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86|archivedate =2015-12-08}}</ref>。

==== 艾米莉亞  ====
